# 8 bpp, tiles, export map, flat layout, set magenta as transparent
-gB8 -gt -m -mLf -gTFFOOFF

# Custom format: Use 16 bit map entries, all 16 bits are the tile index
-mB16:i16

# Only attempt tile reduction, not flip reduction
-mRt

# In this example you can also try to disable tile reduction to push the engine
# to the limit. In that case, the tile usage will always be the maximum.
#-mR!
